OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FReporter Helen Carnell has been to a
OL,8,Ffarm in County Durham where they are
OL,9,Fstruggling to get drinking water to
OL,10,Ftheir livestock
OL,12,FA farm in County Durham is battling
OL,13,Fagainst the freezing weather to ensure
OL,14,Fpregnant cattle and sheep remain fed
OL,15,Fand watered during the cold snap.
OL,17,FStephen Lamb, from Doe Park Farm, in
OL,18,FCotherstone, near Barnard Castle, said
OL,19,Fthe sub-zero temperatures this week
OL,20,Fare unlike anything he has seen for
OL,21,Fdecades.
