OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees: "I'm 60 years
OL,8,Fold, and I can't remember temperatures
OL,9,Flike this here since the 1970s or 80s.
OL,11,F"Farming is very hard going, but it's
OL,12,Fin our blood, since I was a small
OL,13,Fchild all I wanted to do was farm, and
OL,14,FI hope some of my family will want to
OL,15,Fcontinue from me."
OL,17,FStephen is facing challenges to ensure
OL,18,Fthat the roughly 250 sheep on his farm
OL,19,Fcontinue to have access to drinking
OL,20,Fwater.
