OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FHe has had to use a hammer to break
OL,8,Fthick ice on his water troughs, but is
OL,9,Fconcerned the pipes which supply them
OL,10,Fwill also freeze up, and has moved his
OL,11,Fflock closer to a reliable water
OL,12,Fsupply.
OL,14,FMeanwhile in the cattle sheds, boiling
OL,15,Fwater from kettles is being used to
OL,16,Ftry and prevent the pipes from
OL,17,Ffreezing, and buckets have been filled
OL,18,Fwith water in case the supply does
OL,19,Fstop.
