OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FAlison Lamb, who farms the land with
OL,8,Fher husband, said: "A lot of the ewes
OL,9,Fare pregnant at the moment, so
OL,10,Fobviously we need to keep an eye on
OL,11,Ftheir health.
OL,13,F"Some of the cattle are also pregnant,
OL,14,Fthey're due within the next three or
OL,15,Ffour weeks, so obviously feed, water
OL,16,Fand warmth are all really important
OL,17,Ffor them."
