OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FThe North East has experienced a
OL,8,Fparticularly cold start to 2025, with
OL,9,Ftemperatures well below freezing on
OL,10,Fmany days, coupled with blasts of
OL,11,Fheavy snow.
OL,13,FThe Met Office has said the coldest
OL,14,Ftemperature of Wednesday night (8
OL,15,FJanuary) was recorded in Cumbria at
OL,16,Fminus 11.2C. A spokeswoman said they
OL,17,Fare "expecting tonight (Thursday) to
OL,18,Fbe another very cold night".
