OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FAlison added: "Minus 15 is really
OL,8,Fcold, usually we think minus six is a
OL,9,Fbit nippy, it's the extremes of
OL,10,Ftemperature that make it a little bit
OL,11,Fmore unusual.
OL,13,F"I don't think people always
OL,14,Fappreciate what the conditions are
OL,15,Flike for us, and obviously farmers all
OL,16,Fover the country, whatever the
OL,17,Fweather's like you've just got to get
OL,18,Fon with it."
