OL,3,CFarmers struggle to get water to
OL,4,Clivestock during 'worst cold snap in
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FJames Copeland from the National
OL,8,FFarmers' Union said: "Farmers across
OL,9,Fthe North are incredibly resilient,
OL,10,Ftheir priority at the moment is to
OL,11,Fmake sure their business can continue.
OL,13,F"At some point, this snow and ice will
OL,14,Fall be melting, and that will then
OL,15,Fresult in water coming down the
OL,16,Fnetworks, and as we've seen in other
OL,17,Fparts of the country, that's resulted
OL,18,Fin flooding."
